{
  "uuid": "8a6a9600aec129fbb485f0bd8b7697e0",
  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "MENS HAIRDRESSER",
  "description": "<h3><strong>Job Description</strong></h3><p>We are looking for a skilled and professional Men’s Hairdresser to join our team. The ideal candidate has strong barbering skills, a passion for men’s grooming, and excellent customer service. You will be responsible for providing high-quality haircuts, beard grooming, and styling services while maintaining a clean, welcoming salon environment.</p><h3><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></h3><ul><li><p>Perform men’s haircuts, fades, tapers, and classic styles</p></li><li><p>Trim, shape, and style beards and mustaches</p></li><li><p>Provide hair washing, blow-drying, and styling services</p></li><li><p>Consult with clients to understand their preferences and recommend suitable styles</p></li><li><p>Maintain cleanliness and hygiene of tools, equipment, and workstations</p></li><li><p>Ensure a positive customer experience and build client relationships</p></li><li><p>Stay up to date with current men’s grooming trends and techniques</p></li><li><p>Handle appointments and manage time efficiently</p></li></ul><h2><strong>Requirements & Qualifications</strong></h2><ul><li><p>Proven experience as a men’s hairdresser or barber</p></li><li><p>Formal training or certification in hairdressing/barbering (preferred)</p></li><li><p>Strong knowledge of men’s haircuts, beard grooming, and styling techniques</p></li><li><p>Excellent communication and customer service skills</p></li><li><p>Ability to work independently and as part of a team</p></li><li><p>Professional appearance and positive attitude</p></li><li><p>Attention to detail and creativity</p></li><li><p>Knowledge of hygiene and safety standards</p></li></ul><h2><strong>Preferred Skills (Optional)</strong></h2><ul><li><p>Experience with modern styles, skin fades, and hot towel shaves</p></li><li><p>Ability to recommend grooming products</p></li><li><p>Social media or portfolio showcasing previous work</p></li></ul>",
